com.documentum.fc.client.search

Interface IDfValueListAttrExpression

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDfAttrExpression, IDfExpression

    public interface IDfValueListAttrExpression
extends IDfAttrExpression
    Defines a search expression that requires the attribute value to be included in a list of values.
    See Also:
    IDfQueryBuilder.getRootExpressionSet(), IDfExpressionSet.addValueListAttrExpression(String, int, int, boolean, boolean)
